    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 10-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once the potatoes are done, drain and leave them to steam dry, reserving the pot for later</p>",
